# == Class: inspircd::config
#
# Create configuration files for InspIRCd, based on default settings
# from inspircd::params and hiera.
#
# === Parameters
#
# None
#
# === Authors
#
# Evgeni Golov <evgeni@golov.de>
#
# === Copyright
#
